Title: agent_prometheus: fixing cadvisor memory check when no valid memory limit was provided
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1621433821
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

In the previous version, the machine memory was occasionally missing when
the memory limit was 0. This werk fixes this behaviour to always provide
the machine memory for this case.
